  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rrvzh504QlAPoV3ukYPAF19brW3dOZSrn6kOiarkoriaqpFA47UsoZGSIw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505140401\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 578px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54bf6e26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7Rrvzh504QlAPoV3ukYPAF19brW3dOZSrn6kOiarkoriaqpFA47UsoZGSIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：元宇</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AI真能提升编程生产力？还是只会为你挖坑加活？Fastly针对美国开发者，做了一项有关AI生产力的调研，发现高级开发者使用AI交付的代码量是初学者的2.5倍。调研也揭示了AI编码的「隐形成本」——识别和修正AI错误的成本。有时一个小bug，就可能改通宵，效率不增反降。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av88i\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI写代码，真的能提升10倍生产力吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1v93\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">上手飞快，看起来似乎很爽。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avv2f\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但速度与激情背后，AI也会为你挖坑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1rq7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有时，一个不易察觉的小bug，会让你调试半天。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avl29\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">飞速背后，是惊悚的「隐性成本」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">你交付的代码</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">有多少是AI写的？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1w9f\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在Fastly针对美国开发者的一项调研中，发现高级开发者（10年以上经验），使用AI交付的代码量，是初级开发者（0–2年经验）的2.5倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avh51\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">约有1/3的高级开发者表示，他们交付的代码中，AI生成的占到了50%以上，是初级开发者的2.5倍，后者这一比例为13%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505140394\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7266666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1800\" data-height=\"1308\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"408\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3f25721&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrH9QeHmeuO2q5ZDLoicUgwUjPs79SibZ6gm8ktqKS1J1J8o1CIyGLdXaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avyz7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">该调查由Fastly于2025年7月10日至14日开展，共收集了791名职业开发者的反馈</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avprx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位高级开发者结合自己的编程经历，称AI可以在代码测试、找出错误、无缝修复方面比人类更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1f4v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但一位初级开发者却对此表示困惑，他们的问题是不知道如何在编程中驾驭AI，达到预期效果：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「AI总是以为我在做某件事，但事实并不是这样，结果我得自己回头重写。」</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1btu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有59%的高级开发者仍认为AI工具总体上帮助他们更快交付代码，相比之下初级开发者只有49%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1nnc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果显示，高级开发者对AI编程的看法更加乐观。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1xmc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有超过50%的初级开发者表示，AI仅仅让他们「稍微快了一些」，但只有39%的高级开发者这么认为。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1ogr\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比之下，高级开发者更加认同AI让他们的工作加速明显的说法：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">26%的人表示AI让他们「快得多」，是初级开发者（13%）的两倍。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avna8\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而造成这一差距的主要原因，应当在于开发经验上：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通常，高级开发者的经验，让他们更能识别并修正AI的错误。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avib4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们更能识别出「看起来没问题」的代码中是否有坑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av22du\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这让他们在使用AI的过程中更自信也更高效，甚至敢在一些关键业务代码使用AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avvu1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">但初级开发者因为缺乏经验，不能有效识别AI代码中的错误，因此更加谨慎，他们甚至会避免在生产环境中使用AI。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1qyr\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">实际调研数据，也印证了这一点：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1kgn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">只有13%的初级开发者使用AI交付的代码超过50%，而高级开发者中这一比例是32%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avd1o\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明：越是有经验的开发者，在工作中会更加积极使用AI，同时也更信任它们在生产环境中的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av23ad\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">考虑到「氛围编程」（vibe coding，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">即过度依赖&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;随意写代码</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">）可能带来的漏洞，这一发现让更多人意识到：经验在AI编程应用上的重要性。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">提速，还是降速？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">小心「假性进度」陷阱</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1bw3\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然，高级开发者更倾向于使用AI交付代码，但他们之中也有近30%称在修改AI输出上多花费的时间，抵消了大部分节省的时间，而初级开发者中这一比例是17%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1p4u\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">只有14%的开发者，表示他们很少需要改动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1sh7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">尽管如此：仍有超过一半的开发者觉得使用Copilot、Gemini或Claude等AI工具让他们整体更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505140395\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7261111111111112\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1800\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-width=\"1800\" data-height=\"1307\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"408\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85a589c7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2byJeqHyDicLyG0z0wgx7RrgyA36tQYpj4OWt4qfloPib8gcGxX0pEoqiaQVibaButIQiaDN9WNNSgIbg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avsex\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Fastly的这项调研，并非唯一有关「AI提升生产力」的研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av7l\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">还有一些针对资深开发者的随机对照实验（RCT），甚至发现：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652608967&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=e6068b7d6ff9c2b1edb5a66e5e5c4482&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"当开发者使用AI工具时，他们完成任务的时间反而增加了19%。\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">当开发者使用AI工具时，他们完成任务的时间反而增加了19%。</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1ctl\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种反差背后，可能和心理感觉有关。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1yb2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">用AI写代码，一开始可能会觉得很爽，只用敲几下，代码就可以补全。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avf3a\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这很容易让人掉入这种「假性进度」的陷阱：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然开始速度飞快，但随后频繁的修改、测试和返工常把这些优势消耗掉。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1cvl\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Fastly与开发者的一些交流，以及调查反馈的评论，都反映了这种情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1h9n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位受访者表示，「虽然像GitHub Copilot这样的AI工具能建议代码片段甚至完整函数，对我帮助很大，但有一次用它生成了一个看似正确的复杂算法，结果一个暗藏的细微bug，让我调试了好几个小时。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av9y\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">也有受访者表示，AI虽然能够省下写样板代码的时间，但也会带来一些效率低下的问题，需要手动修复，最后速度就被拉回来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1e9m\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI可能会省事，但也可能给你「加活」，从而抵消了它效率提升的一面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1y2l\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">调研发现，除了提效之外，AI的另一项作用是提供「情绪价值」，可以增加开发工作的乐趣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av11q9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">有将近80%的开发者表示AI工具让编程变得更享受：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人觉得可以跳过枯燥的重复劳动，有人则喜欢那种即时生成代码带来的满足感。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avi3v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">还有的受访者表示，AI可以帮忙突破被卡住的任务，帮自己找到完成任务所需的答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av1uig\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然快乐不等于效率，但AI带来的这种积极的情绪价值，还是十分必要的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">注意AI编码的「隐性成本」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avkzk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">Fastly还调研了开发者对绿色编码（green coding，即节能软件编写方式）以及AI工具能耗的认知。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avjzo\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">调研表明，开发者随着经验增长，绿色编码的实践率也在明显提高：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">超过56%的初级开发者说他们会主动考虑能耗，而中高级开发者中这一比例接近80%。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41av19d0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发者们对于AI工具的环境成本，也有清楚的认识：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大约三分之二的开发者，表示他们知道这些工具会带来可观的碳排放；即使在初级开发者中，只有8%表示完全不了解。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0m41avwkj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明，绿色编程的理念，已逐渐成为开发者文化的一部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.fastly.com/blog/senior-developers-ship-more-ai-code\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fastly.com/blog/senior-developers-ship-more-ai-code</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Fastly 调研揭示高级开发者使用 AI 代码交付量是初级开发者 2.5 倍，但 AI 编码存在“隐性成本”和“假性进度”陷阱，经验是有效利用 AI 的关键。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Fastly 调研揭示高级开发者使用 AI 代码交付量是初级开发者 2.5 倍，但 AI 编码存在“隐性成本”和“假性进度”陷阱，经验是有效利用 AI 的关键。",
  "summary": "文章基于 Fastly 对美国 791 名开发者进行的调研，深入分析了 AI 对编程生产力的影响。调研发现，拥有 10 年以上经验的高级开发者使用 AI 交付的代码量是初级开发者的 2.5 倍，且对 AI 工具的积极性和信任度更高。然而，文章也指出 AI 编码存在“隐性成本”，即识别和修正 AI 错误所花费的时间可能抵消初始效率提升，甚至导致任务完成时间增加。这种“假性进度”陷阱尤其对缺乏经验的初级开发者影响更大。尽管如此，AI 工具仍能提供“情绪价值”，通过自动化重复性劳动、即时代码生成等方式，提升编程的乐趣。文章还提及了开发者对绿色编码和 AI 能耗的认知，显示经验越丰富的开发者越关注能耗问题。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "高级开发者 AI 代码交付量远超初级开发者，且更乐观",
      "explanation": "资深开发者因经验丰富，能有效识别并修正 AI 生成的错误，从而更自信、高效地利用 AI 工具，交付更多代码并感受到显著的效率提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 编码存在“隐性成本”和“假性进度”陷阱",
      "explanation": "AI 生成的代码可能包含不易察觉的 bug，导致长时间的调试和返工，这可能抵消了初期提速的优势，甚至降低整体开发效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 为编程提供“情绪价值”，提升工作乐趣",
      "explanation": "AI 工具能够自动化枯燥的重复劳动，提供即时代码生成，并帮助开发者突破卡点，从而增加编程的享受感和积极性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 真能提升编程生产力？还是只会为你挖坑加活？",
    "有时，一个不易察觉的小 bug，会让你调试半天。飞速背后，是惊悚的「隐性成本」。",
    "高级开发者的经验，让他们更能识别并修正 AI 的错误。他们更能识别出「看起来没问题」的代码中是否有坑。",
    "虽然开始速度飞快，但随后频繁的修改、测试和返工常把这些优势消耗掉。",
    "有将近 80%的开发者表示 AI 工具让编程变得更享受"
  ],
